### WARNING
### This file changes local development data.
### Requests are additive and may create shipments.
### Shipping a shipment calls Ordering and marks the linked order as Shipped.
### Current MVP behavior: Inventory reservation is already committed by Ordering mark-paid.
### Ordering API must be running and configured through OrderingApi:BaseUrl.
### Change runId before running the full flow again.

@FulfillmentApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5006
@OrderingApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5002
@CatalogApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001
@InventoryApi_HostAddress = http://localhost:5003

@runId = 001
@productVariantId = 9572fb9d-f059-401e-9041-7fc75f8cb414
@sku = ARM-BLK


### Health check
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/health


### Create paid order for shipment flow
# @name createOrderForShipment
POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Shipment Flow Customer {{runId}}",
  "customerEmail": "shipment-flow-{{runId}}@example.com",
  "items": [
    {
      "productVariantId": "{{productVariantId}}",
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}


### Mark order as paid
@orderId = {{createOrderForShipment.response.body.$.id}}

POST {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}/mark-paid


### Create shipment for paid order
# @name createShipment
POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "{{orderId}}",
  "carrier": "Manual",
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-{{runId}}"
}


### Get created shipment
@shipmentId = {{createShipment.response.body.$.id}}

GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentId}}


### Ship shipment and mark order as shipped
POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentId}}/ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrier": "Manual",
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-SHIPPED-{{runId}}"
}


### Get shipment after ship
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentId}}


### Get order after shipment shipped
GET {{OrderingApi_HostAddress}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}


### Check Inventory stock after shipment shipped
### Current MVP behavior: stock should not change here because mark-paid already committed reservation.
GET {{InventoryApi_HostAddress}}/api/stock/{{sku}}


### Ship already shipped shipment should return 400
POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentId}}/ship
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "carrier": "Manual",
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-RETRY-{{runId}}"
}


### Create shipment for cancel flow
# @name createShipmentForCancel
POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "carrier": "Manual",
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-CANCEL-{{runId}}"
}


### Cancel pending shipment
@shipmentToCancelId = {{createShipmentForCancel.response.body.$.id}}

POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentToCancelId}}/cancel


### Get cancelled shipment
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/{{shipmentToCancelId}}


### Create invalid shipment without order id should return 400
POST {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "carrier": "Manual",
  "trackingNumber": "TRACK-INVALID"
}


### Missing shipment should return 404
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000


### List shipments
GET {{FulfillmentApi_HostAddress}}/api/shipments
